		explode boom4 type EXPLODE_ON_HIT | FIRE | FALL;
		explode boom5 type EXPLODE_ON_HIT | FIRE | FALL;
		explode boom6 type EXPLODE_ON_HIT | FIRE | SMOKE | FALL;
